#: ../../includes_lwrp/includes_lwrp_sudo.rst:6
# 4c7b56389187468083450b82f33ec8b6
msgid "Natural mode mimics the |sudo cmd| file interface. This mode will render a |sudo cmd| fragment in |path etc sudoers d|"
